程序包 inkball

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    App  
    Ball
    The Ball class represents a ball in the game with properties such as position, velocity, and color.
    BallManager
    The BallManager class manages a list of all ball colors of the level.
    GameConfig
    The GameConfig class handles the configuration settings for the game.
    Level
    The Level class represents a game level in the Inkball game.
    LevelDisplay
    The LevelDisplay class manages the loading and representation of a game level.
    Line
    The Line class represents a line made up of a series of points.
    Tile
    The Tile class represents a tile on the game board.
    Vec
    The Vec class represents a 2D vector with x and y components.
